SAP 
Everything in SAP is a Transaction.A Transaction is a 
specific task for performing an activity.SAP is a 
Transaction based system. A client is a unique global entity 
having its own set of data.800 is the client no for learning 
SAP.
SAP Easy Access is the tool for learning SAP.
It is called as SAP IDES which stands for Internet 
Demonstration and Education System.
SE --- Software engineering/development
SM --- System maintenance
ST --- System Trace
The following are some of the important transaction codes 
that are commonly used in ABAP:
SE11 --- ABAP Dictionary
SE38 --- ABAP Editor
SE37 --- Function Builder
SE51 --- Screen Painter
SE41 --- Menu Painter
SE80 --- Object Navigator
SE71 --- Form Painter
SE21 --- Package Builder
SE14 --- Database Utilities 
Note:All the user defined or custom defined objects created 
by the developer should begin with "Z" or "Y" only.
